EX 1TB 7200RPM 3.5\t<br />\n<br />\nSharkoon 擎天者 BW9000-W ATX &mdash; White\t<br />\n<br />\nASUS PCE-AC56 Wi-Fi PCI-E\t<br />\n<br />\nG.Skill Aegis Gaming Series 8GB (1 x 8GB) DDR4 2800MHz C17 F4-2800C17S-8GIS\t<br />\n<br />\nSamsung PM961 Polaris 256GB M.2 PCIe NVMe 3.0 x4<br />\n<br />\nTotal: ~$7400</blockquote><br />\n依家轉埋msi gaming x 1070 同550w neoco II火牛"},{"pid":"cc56a6850cf07f0b670056377aa0f620889b1aa3","tid":430413,"uid":20942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>二手要唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差唔多spec</blockquote><br />\n應該就唔會 不過你咩spec同放咩價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n7700<br />\nCooler master hyper 212 led turbo cpu cooler<br />\nGigabyte b250m d3h<br />\n1070<br />\n2400 MHz 8gb ram x2<br />\nAntec 550w bronze <br />\nSeagate 2tb hdd<br />\nSamsung 960 evo 240gb ssd<br />\nSharkoon bw9000 黑色<br />\n<br />\n好似係咁<br />\n好享受砌機既過程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打放幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留個tg傾下</blockquote><br />\n都係算啦 電話冇位del咗tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋都想買過set新嘅</blockquote><br />\n岩既，自己砌幾爽"},{"pid":"e287196ef07129de6429c9816cef09d33bc8f9aa","tid":430413,"uid":18825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>二手要唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差唔多spec</blockquote><br />\n應該就唔會 不過你咩spec同放咩價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n7700<br />\nCooler master hyper 212 led turbo cpu cooler<br />\nGigabyte b250m d3h<br />\n1070<br />\n2400 MHz 8gb ram x2<br />\nAntec 550w bronze <br />\nSeagate 2tb hdd<br />\nS